videos.description: Michigan guard Zavier Simpson drives to the basket and tosses up a hook shot that goes in off the glass.
videos.headline: Simpson banks in hook shot

videos.description: Michigan center Jon Teske puts up a 3-pointer that bounces off the back and front of the rim and still goes in.
videos.headline: Teske gets lucky bounce on 3-pointer

videos.description: Michigan guard Jordan Poole sends a pass downcourt to a sprinting Jon Teske, who drops in the easy layup.
videos.headline: Poole finds a sprinting Teske for layup

videos.description: Michigan guard Zavier Simpson tosses a pass ahead to Isaiah Livers, who drives for a thunderous one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Livers flies in for one-handed hammer

videos.description: Wisconsin's D'Mitrik Trice passes the ball to Ethan Happ, who rises up for a powerful one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Happ elevates for big dunk

videos.description: After Wisconsin blocks a shot and Nate Reuvers throws down a dunk, Brad Davison seals the Badgers' upset of No. 2 Michigan with another steal.
videos.headline: Dunk, steal clinch Wisconsin's upset of Michigan

videos.description: The Wisconsin crowd celebrates on the court after the Badgers take down No. 2 Michigan 64-54.
videos.headline: Wisconsin fans storm the court after upsetting Michigan
